node.text:
The weekend. No Teams meetings. No email. No HBL. Trying to be disciplined. Clear line between work and home.
.
Time to declutter the house. Found this photo taken right after the nikah (marriage solemnisation).
.
Ah, how young and naive.😆
.
Photo looks a century old. Has it been that long?!
.
Either that, or it was a drama series about a young couple in a past life & their melodramatic adventures. (We’ve been watching too many Kdramas. The Goblin, anyone? Or The King?)
.
#backtobasics #declutter #refresh #ramadan2020 #circuitbreakersg
